long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 1209906 Eclipse error log file
Description of problem: For current Fedora 25, eclipse fails to start up. Instead, an error message pops up pointing to a log file which is attached to this bug report.
Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable): eclipse-4.6.1-2.fc25
How reproducible: Always
Steps to Reproduce: 1. Run 'eclipse' in a shell.
Actual results: After presenting the greeter, an error window pops up.
Expected results: Eclipse starts up successfully.
Additional info: No corresponding entry is found in the bug reporting tool.
